{"tid":1310330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【資訊類】聽日有賣旗活動","createTime":"2019-07-12T15:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T15:47:00.000Z","uid":239384,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f7fb881739383d88a38f10448f59013b6910cff1","tid":1310330,"uid":239384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:21:25.000Z","msg":"聽日<span style=\"color: red;\">九龍區</span>有<span style=\"color: blue;\">觀塘民聯會</span>嘅賣旗活動wor<br />\n作為良好市民當然應該當仁不讓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過正所謂冇原則嘅善良無異於作惡 所以行善之前我地應該瞭解清楚情況再作決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你都有以下疑問 記得問清楚幫手募捐嘅義工 先再決定捐唔捐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似冇聽過你地呢個機構wor 係做咩架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地係咩機構可唔可以講少少背景資料？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地之前搞過咩活動架？未來會有咩活動？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知多D可以令我地對該機構嘅運作有更多嘅瞭解 從而對機構有更高信心 對機構身份存疑但又有興趣做善事嘅巴絲記得問多兩句啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日籌到嘅錢你地會點用架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時同邊度可以睇翻筆錢用左係邊？有冇電話或者網址果D比我睇翻呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />畢竟慈善機構應該對捐款人負責同承擔責任 你嘅錢用左係邊你有權知！ 唔洗急 睇過(過去嘅)財務報表再決定捐唔捐錢都未遲架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係義工定係本身係機構職員？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地嘅活動歡唔歡迎公眾參與？如果我對參與你地嘅活動/做義工有興趣我可以點樣搵到你地嘅資訊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你聽完對呢個機構好有好感 想落手落腳做慈善呀！記得唔好怕醜 問下義工啦！<br />\n<br />\n最後記得賣旗日法定時間係<span style=\"color: red;\">上午七時至下午十二時三十分</span> 想做慈善嘅巴絲千祈唔好錯過啦 過左就冇得買架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n閱讀更多:<br />\n二零一九至二零年度全港區賣旗日公開籌款許可證的發證條件<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/storage/asset/section/1576/tc/Flag_Day_19-20_Permit_Conditions_20190412.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Fstorage%2Fasset%2Fsection%2F1576%2Ftc%2FFlag_Day_19-20_Permit_Conditions_20190412.pdf&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=69143fa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/storage/asset/section/1576/tc/Flag_Day_19-20_Permit_Conditions_20190412.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n慈善籌款良好實務指引<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/theme/fundraising/docs/good_practice_guide.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Ftheme%2Ffundraising%2Fdocs%2Fgood_practice_guide.pdf&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=dd64501a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/theme/fundraising/docs/good_practice_guide.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"c27bffc00b3c96ad43f17cc181729d2c5cadf299","tid":1310330,"uid":239384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"32550213787c58ceb45d2fbed19b045fc8487cc6","tid":1310330,"uid":239384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:25:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"381b263e3d51fd96934d90b4e04a83417c2d117b","tid":1310330,"uid":239384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:26:28.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cff97c4674b201d6db9624db1b70acf4b574ef01","tid":1310330,"uid":239384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:28:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0953d3a6a9cd573e74d8233f35fbc8b76999dd54","tid":1310330,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:29:04.000Z","msg":"拒絕買旗"},{"pid":"47824ab21ac0ace4db6469e1e3327cd3b28e7aff","tid":1310330,"uid":239384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0953d3a6a9cd573e74d8233f35fbc8b76999dd54","tid":1310330,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:29:04.